# Note: Ordering matters here: The 'werk new' command still displays 'compat' and 'incompat'
# as choices to the user, but acts on the real config. To be agnostic of the config and 'yes' and
# 'no' as strings, the first element always maps to 'compat' and the second to 'incompat'.
